& [InferenceJobResult] is boundary delineation proposal
  + [focus] is local model worker proposals
  + [inside] is non-mutating SOP content
  + [boundary] is authority separation rule
  + [outside] is integration decisions beyond scope
  + [inference] is Codex retains control
  + [caution] is avoid autonomous code changes
  + [next_step] is submit SOP for review